<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Rock Gaming NL — Built on the Rock. Gaming Everywhere.</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Barlow:wght@400;600;700&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --red: #e63946;
    --gold: #f4c430;
    --blue: #1d3557;
    --light-blue: #457b9d;
    --white: #f1faee;
    --dark: #0a0e1a;
    --darker: #060810;
    --card: #111827;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--darker);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NOISE OVERLAY */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(6, 8, 16, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.2);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .nav-logo span { color: var(--red); }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--red); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(69, 123, 157, 0.2) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, rgba(29, 53, 87, 0.3) 0%, transparent 60%),
      var(--darker);
  }

  .hero-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    animation: gridMove 20s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes gridMove {
    0% { transform: translateY(0); }
    100% { transform: translateY(60px); }
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--red);
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0% 100%);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero h1 .line1 { color: var(--white); }
  .hero h1 .line2 { color: var(--red); }
  .hero h1 .line3 { 
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.7);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .hero-sub strong { color: var(--gold); }

  .hero-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--red);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    clip-path: polygon(12px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 12px) 100%, 0% 100%);
    transition: all 0.2s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #ff4757;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 2px solid rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.3);
    clip-path: polygon(12px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 12px) 100%, 0% 100%);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* STATS BAR */
  .stats-bar {
    background: var(--red);
    padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
    padding-left: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-title span { color: var(--red); }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.75);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .about-text p strong { color: var(--gold); }

  .about-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.2);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .about-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 3px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--red);
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--red);
  }

  .about-card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* STREAMER PROGRAM */
  .streamer-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.08) 0%, rgba(29, 53, 87, 0.2) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.2);
    padding: 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 0 -2rem;
  }

  .streamer-section::before {
    content: 'STREAM';
    position: absolute;
    right: -2rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(90deg);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12rem;
    color: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.04);
    pointer-events: none;
    letter-spacing: 10px;
  }

  .streamer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .perks-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .perks-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
  }

  .perk-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .perk-text h4 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .perk-text p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.6);
  }

  /* PHASES */
  .phases {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .phase {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .phase-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--red);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 3rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .phase-content h4 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .phase-content p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* PLATFORMS */
  .platforms-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .platform-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .platform-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--red);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .platform-card:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .platform-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3);
    background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.9);
  }

  .platform-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .platform-name {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .platform-handle {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.5);
  }

  /* COMMUNITY */
  .community-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .community-section .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .community-desc {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .community-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .feature-emoji {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .feature-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--red);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-section::before {
    content: 'JOIN';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20rem;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    pointer-events: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    letter-spacing: 20px;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative;
  }

  .btn-white {
    background: white;
    color: var(--red);
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    clip-path: polygon(12px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 12px) 100%, 0% 100%);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-white:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .btn-dark {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    clip-path: polygon(12px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 12px) 100%, 0% 100%);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-dark:hover {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--darker);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.2);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-logo span { color: var(--red); }

  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.5);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--red); }

  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(241, 250, 238, 0.25);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3), transparent);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .streamer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .about-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .streamer-section { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; margin: 0 -1rem; }
    section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  }

  /* SCROLL ANIMATIONS */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }

  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">ROCK<span>GAMING</span>NL</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#streamers">Streamers</a></li>
    <li><a href="#community">Community</a></li>
    <li><a href="#platforms">Find Us</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://discord.gg/EgkJRwSbWs" target="_blank">Join Discord</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">🌊 Newfoundland & Labrador</div>
    <h1>
      <div class="line1">ROCK</div>
      <div class="line2">GAMING</div>
      <div class="line3">NL</div>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      <strong>Built on the Rock. Gaming Everywhere.</strong><br>
      NL's first dedicated gaming community hub — connecting players, showcasing streamers, and putting the province on the map.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="https://discord.gg/EgkJRwSbWs" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Join Discord</a>
      <a href="#streamers" class="btn-secondary">Streamer Program</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Discord Members</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-number">150+</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Facebook Followers</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-number">5</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Platforms</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-number">18+</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Community</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-number">1</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Week Old 🔥</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid reveal">
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-tag">Who We Are</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">NL'S <span>GAMING</span> HUB</h2>
      <p>Rock Gaming NL isn't just a Discord server — we're building <strong>Newfoundland and Labrador's first full gaming community platform.</strong></p>
      <p>Whether you stream, watch, play casually, or grind competitively — if you're from the Rock, you belong here. We're connecting local players, shining a spotlight on NL content creators, and putting this province on the gaming map.</p>
      <p>Nobody was doing this for NL. <strong>So we built it.</strong></p>
      <br>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/EgkJRwSbWs" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Join The Community</a>
    </div>
    <div class="about-cards">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">🎮</div>
        <h4>All Platforms</h4>
        <p>PC, Xbox, PlayStation — we don't gatekeep here.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">🌊</div>
        <h4>NL Proud</h4>
        <p>Built by Newfoundlanders for Newfoundlanders.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">📺</div>
        <h4>Creator Support</h4>
        <p>We promote and grow NL streamers across all platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">🔞</div>
        <h4>18+ Community</h4>
        <p>Mature, respectful, good vibes only.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- STREAMER PROGRAM -->
<div class="streamer-section" id="streamers">
  <div class="streamer-grid reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="section-tag">For Creators</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">STREAMER <span>PROGRAM</span></h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(241,250,238,0.7); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">Whether you've never streamed before or you're already building your audience — Rock Gaming NL has your back. We provide the platform, the promotion, and the community.</p>
      <ul class="perks-list">
        <li>
          <span class="perk-icon">🔑</span>
